<section class="relative pb-16 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="mt-8 container mx-auto px-4 ">
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-black tracking-tight mb-6">
          依照車型，選擇不同固定方式 !
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <image class=" mx-auto hidden md:block" src="{{ 'banner12.png'|file_url }}"></image>
    <image class=" mx-auto md:hidden" src="{{ 'banner12_mobile.png'|file_url }}"></image>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-16 md:max-w-[70%] mx-auto px-4 ">
    <div class="rounded-lg  flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
      <p class="font-heading text-xl xs:text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl  text-black tracking-tight font-bold">
        加購車充專用支架
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8 mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-lg col-start-1 mx-auto">
        <image src="{{ 'display1.png'|file_url }}"></image>
        <p class="text-center font-bold text-lg py-2">吸盤式通用支架</p>
        <p class="text-center text-base px-8">不挑車款、黏性佳、極穩固，無痕強力黏膠可水洗清潔，吸力不減</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg  mx-auto">
        <image src="{{ 'display2.png'|file_url }}"></image>
        <p class="text-center font-bold text-lg py-2">Tesla 電動車出風口支架</p>
        <p class="text-center text-base px-8">質感金屬太空灰，穩固不易搖晃，特殊鎖勾旋轉固定設計，簡易安裝方便拆卸</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg  mx-auto">
        <image src="{{ 'display3.png'|file_url }}"></image>
        <p class="text-center font-bold text-lg py-2">圓形專用出風口支架</p>
        <p class=" text-base  text-center px-8">適用圓形出風口，伸縮設計，不傷出風口葉片，輕鬆好安裝</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
